text: Heliophanus thaleri is a jumping spider species in the genus Heliophanus. It was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 2009 and lives in South Africa. ==References== Category:Salticidae Category:Spiders of South Africa Category:Spiders described in 2009 Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
title: Heliophanus thaleri
